Аs a customer, I want to set the desired parameters and for the system to remember them so that I do not set them every time and save my time

As a customer, I want to have an account where i can always login so my data is saved and i would not have to type in my data every time

As a customer, I want to set the desired parameters and for the system to find me a sample for them, so that I can buy the desired watch

Аs a customer, I want the system to find the watch itself and send me a message so that I can buy the desired watch faster

As a customer, I want to be able to specify the brand, reference number, land, color, model and price of the watch in the parameters to get a suitable selection for me

As a customer, I want to receive notifications only when new search results appear, so that I can pay attention to these notifications without taking them for spam

Аs a customer, I want the interface to be clear and not require extra effort to configure the search parameters so that I use this service

